Package: RNAlocate
Type: Package
Title: Identify mobile RNA molecules in plant graft systems 
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Katie", "Jeynes-Cupper", email = "katie.jeynescupper@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Marco", "Catoni", email = "m.catoni@bham.ac.uk", role = "aut"))
Description: The relocate package allows for the identifcation of mobile small 
 interfering RNA molecules (siRNA) derived from one genotype which have travelled 
 into another genotype via a graft junction in a hetero-graft plant system.  
 The package allows users to pre-process and analyse sRNA-seq data in this context with the end goal of identifying mobile siRNAs and their potential function or implications on phenotypic changes. 
